dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded as a shapefile by ITOS from HDX. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following errors were found and fixed: 1. Created and populated reference name field 2. Admin2 name "Saint louis du Sud" was made Proper Case 3. Fixed multipart slivers in units "2e Section La Vallee de Bainet ou Ternier" and "2e Section des Varreux"
The following was found but not addressed in this version: 1. Creole Admin2 and 3 names are not included. The documentation sent with the original shapefiles lists them as "UNAVAILABLE". 2. Admin2 and 3 English and French names are mostly identical. The "English" names are simply the French names without accented characters.
